Headquartered in the greater Hartford city of New Britain, Connecticut, Stanley Black & Decker is the result of the merger of Stanley Works and Black & Decker on March 12, 2010.
Address: 1000 STANLEY DR, P O BOX 7000, NEW BRITAIN, CT, US
